data.description: Seller will contribute up to $10,000 for loan Buy-Down or closing costs! This split foyer beauty is loaded with upgrades with space for everyone.  There are 3 bedrooms and 2 baths on the main level with a vaulted great room open to the kitchen and dining room.  There is a fireplace at the center of the great room and an open kitchen just steps to the entertainer's deck with covered and uncovered portions.  The lower level features a large media room or teen suite plus one bedroom and a bath.  The main house features a large 3 car attached garage and out back there is a detached (38' by 26') 3 car garage for all your toys.  There is even a hydraulic lift for the automobile enthusiast.  Above the detached garage there is a 380 sf bonus room with air conditioning.  Out back there is a fenced yard with garden space and shed. All this and only 15 minutes to Athens and 15 minutes to Commerce.
